{"tid":1168560,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人食野會盡量避免食有骨既野","createTime":"2019-05-23T18:13:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-24T05:47:26.000Z","uid":49197,"like":74,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"de1e570e9cab3127ecfc3de592ed1659da6af011","tid":1168560,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T18:13:59.000Z","msg":"由細到大鯁過幾次骨,自此之後每次食有骨既野都會好認真妹清楚<br />\n後尾索性唔撚食有骨野,堅決唔食魚(除咗酒樓蒸果D貴魚可能食),唔食雞鴨鵝(當然淨雞肉/雞扒會食)<br />\n因為次次都要妹清楚既話會好晒時間,同埋撈落其他食物度好易唔覺意食咗D碎骨,加上食野要就住就住一d都唔爽<br />\n有冇人都係一樣唸法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcabed9f191c9c0a490447b220d9cc9ffcd65fe9","tid":1168560,"uid":245250,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T18:17:02.000Z","msg":"唔食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但因為懶得 簡骨"},{"pid":"06c2bfc0605e54c901cd5edb6278f3520fcdba7d","tid":1168560,"uid":204537,"like":13,"dislike":6,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T18:18:28.000Z","msg":"斬腳趾避沙蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁樣落去唔係辦法<br />\n你細路哥就話唔識野唔知邊啲野有骨<br />\n係唔係都求其咬落去<br />\n但係你依家咁大個人 有啲分析力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n知道咩野有骨跟住試下慢慢食"},{"pid":"fe21c803a5b565f41fd27a8590842fb22b6ba9a5","tid":1168560,"uid":153201,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T18:22:45.000Z","msg":"屌   我同樓主諗法完全一樣 ，但成日比人話仲細咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e61ddac27ad97bd971707488c7770691e1feeee","tid":1168560,"uid":49197,"like":17,"dislike":7,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"fe21c803a5b565f41fd27a8590842fb22b6ba9a5","tid":1168560,"uid":153201,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T18:22:45.000Z","msg":"屌   我同樓主諗法完全一樣 ，但成日比人話仲細咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T18:30:18.000Z","msg":"唔關細唔細路事,要lur骨就肯定浪費多咗時間同注意力,食又食得無咁盡興<br />\n食野主要都係為咗生存+愉悅感,根本唔一定要食有骨野"},{"pid":"dc81b5b99208290144df9dc658ad7e9d7b674b96","tid":1168560,"uid":62841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T18:30:42.000Z","msg":"有殼先煩"},{"pid":"85544228252f1132540221320c37e9774bde7617","tid":1168560,"uid":194525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc81b5b99208290144df9dc658ad7e9d7b674b96","tid":1168560,"uid":62841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T18:30:42.000Z","msg":"有殼先煩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T18:42:58.000Z","msg":"蟹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beb69fe950a202eea999ca32f57b1062422e2327","tid":1168560,"uid":33429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T18:46:36.000Z","msg":"燒味飯之類比較乾嘅嘢我無咩所謂<br />\n但完全接受唔到湯麵/咖哩+有骨嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時啲雞骨斬到碎曬，溝咗落湯入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7d8bf6d792c644951fbefbcab7e40ccedb4659e","tid":1168560,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"beb69fe950a202eea999ca32f57b1062422e2327","tid":1168560,"uid":33429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T18:46:36.000Z","msg":"燒味飯之類比較乾嘅嘢我無咩所謂<br />\n但完全接受唔到湯麵/咖哩+有骨嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時啲雞骨斬到碎曬，溝咗落湯入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T18:53:38.000Z","msg":"燒味飯睇師傅刀法囉...無咩碎骨既話都ok既,有既話都好煩下<br />\n流質野入面有骨係勁煩,除咗易溝咗落去之外,仲好難睇倒D骨既位置,飲湯本身意識防備又通常比較低"},{"pid":"bdfd0ae4b940c2f36af7d0d7866fd2ad296d2d32","tid":1168560,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7d8bf6d792c644951fbefbcab7e40ccedb4659e","tid":1168560,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"beb69fe950a202eea999ca32f57b1062422e2327","tid":1168560,"uid":33429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T18:46:36.000Z","msg":"燒味飯之類比較乾嘅嘢我無咩所謂<br />\n但完全接受唔到湯麵/咖哩+