:"73b19635496900b8d14851f38337989a82497640","tid":1168560,"uid":7763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T03:37:53.000Z","msg":"好撚痴線<br />\n食無骨雞腳?"},{"pid":"5fc13e7c4e60d54bfd3b699db6218e56891aa613","tid":1168560,"uid":202051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T03:39:50.000Z","msg":"有碎骨會唔食<br />\n一諗到條脷掂到骨髓就覺得好嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最撚憎豬骨粥呢啲好多碎骨<br />\n雞翼呢啲都ok<br />\n多骨魚都係盡量唔食"},{"pid":"73d3f74d7a17cf96a0eeb61878e366a1e1c09115","tid":1168560,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T03:40:08.000Z","msg":"食啲一隻匙羹就食得晒嘅野就最滿足<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要lur骨同整污糟手嘅都不了"},{"pid":"5e5f417dc60248c04120abfd597393867bc5e5d3","tid":1168560,"uid":168513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T03:41:04.000Z","msg":"成日俾人話我唔識食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食蟹我除咗啲蟹膏之外<br />\n其他地方都麻麻哋又嘥時間去剝殼"},{"pid":"2cf6bb8e19900d73a8c72bd66bdd6e99489dbc28","tid":1168560,"uid":40468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T03:41:35.000Z","msg":"我由細到大都唔食魚<br />\n聽阿媽講<br />\n係因為幼稚園讀全日制嘅時候<br />\n下晝飯有魚我哽親 之後就由勁鍾意食魚變做唔肯食魚<br />\n雖然我冇哽親嘅印象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過出街我都盡量唔食有骨嘅嘢<br />\n因為好冇儀態同埋會食到好污糟<br />\n又唔係度度都有碟俾你放骨<br />\n就咁放喺枱上面其實勁嘔心"},{"pid":"49bd84e539d4d05c4a24b6ba30c9e238af024538","tid":1168560,"uid":7763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e5f417dc60248c04120abfd597393867bc5e5d3","tid":1168560,"uid":168513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T03:41:04.000Z","msg":"成日俾人話我唔識食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食蟹我除咗啲蟹膏之外<br />\n其他地方都麻麻哋又嘥時間去剝殼"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T03:42:00.000Z","msg":"食多幾次基本上就識<br />\n手腳屈一屈成條肉出晒來"},{"pid":"fb6b02fd61dfb3f3267dacfaba92a5ba1e360b54","tid":1168560,"uid":40468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e5f417dc60248c04120abfd597393867bc5e5d3","tid":1168560,"uid":168513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T03:41:04.000Z","msg":"成日俾人話我唔識食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食蟹我除咗啲蟹膏之外<br />\n其他地方都麻麻哋又嘥時間去剝殼"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T03:42:27.000Z","msg":"我都淨係食蟹膏<br />\n就咁拎住個蟹蓋用匙羹食好方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b62103779aa253e37fe2e4d59005abfcd835d97","tid":1168560,"uid":61511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T03:42:57.000Z","msg":"但多骨既魚真係好食好多既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n細細條果D"},{"pid":"191261f4364970d37b9fd0742c382a4569cea7d9","tid":1168560,"uid":3649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T03:46:14.000Z","msg":"我認真諗過我命格係唔係忌魚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n細個俾骨鯁過勁多次，<br />\n之後都盡量揀啖啖肉得一條大骨嘅魚食。<br />\n<br />\n好啦，食個鰻魚切粒嘅蓋飯，<br />\n吞咗一大啖落去發覺入面喉嚨位勁痛，<br />\n原來有條鰻魚骨插咗落喉嚨肉...<br />\n<br />\n結果要去醫院抆返出嚟 <br />\n嗰陣真係痛撚到喊晒口 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"737ae295f0d54c448c4b750ddbff4699890c40b8","tid":1168560,"uid":1018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T03:52:14.000Z","msg":"食食下雞翼條骨斷開一半 我都會唔食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好怕個種感覺"}]}